        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Patients' Right to Know Their Medication Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Food and Drug Administration to regulate the authorship, content, format, color, printing, and dissemination of patient medication information that is required to be in the labeling of prescription drugs.</p>]]></text>
